<blockquote>&ldquo;D<small>EAR</small> J<small>OHN</small>: Come around as soon as you can. I have news for you. Your uncle, 
<right>&ldquo;S<small>IMON</small> R<small>ICH</small>.&rdquo;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
